<text id="02-output-contract" title="Claude API Integration Record Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the integration-record artefact the methodology emits. Describes which API features the integration code uses so an auditor / cost-tracker can replay the spec.</summary>

  <section title="JSON Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/claude-api-integration.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["artefact_id", "model", "max_tokens", "shape", "retry", "caching", "tooling", "version", "last_reviewed"],
  "properties": {
    "artefact_id":   {"type": "string", "pattern": "^cai-[a-z0-9-]{6,}$"},
    "model":         {"enum": ["claude-haiku-4-5", "claude-sonnet-4-6", "claude-opus-4-7"]},
    "max_tokens":    {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 32000},
    "shape":         {"enum": ["sync", "streaming", "tool-loop", "batch"]},
    "max_turns":     {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 50},
    "retry": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["enabled", "max_attempts", "strategy"],
      "properties": {
        "enabled":      {"type": "boolean"},
        "max_attempts": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 10},
        "strategy":     {"enum": ["exponential-jitter", "linear", "none"]}
      }
    },
    "caching": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["enabled"],
      "properties": {
        "enabled":         {"type": "boolean"},
        "block_token_size":{"type": "integer", "minimum": 0},
        "ttl_seconds":     {"enum": [300, 3600]},
        "prefix_position": {"enum": ["system", "first-content-block"]}
      }
    },
    "tooling": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "tool_count":    {"type": "integer", "minimum": 0, "maximum": 10},
        "forced_tool":   {"type": "boolean"},
        "schema_validation": {"type": "boolean"}
      }
    },
    "extended_thinking": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "enabled":       {"type": "boolean"},
        "budget_tokens": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1024, "maximum": 32000}
      }
    },
    "secrets_source": {"enum": ["env", "1password", "aws-secrets-manager", "vault"]},
    "version":       {"type": "string", "pattern": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$"},
    "last_reviewed": {"type": "string", "format": "date"}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "artefact_id": "cai-rag-summariser",
  "model": "claude-sonnet-4-6",
  "max_tokens": 4096,
  "shape": "tool-loop",
  "max_turns": 10,
  "retry": {"enabled": true, "max_attempts": 5, "strategy": "exponential-jitter"},
  "caching": {"enabled": true, "block_token_size": 2400, "ttl_seconds": 300, "prefix_position": "system"},
  "tooling": {"tool_count": 3, "forced_tool": false, "schema_validation": true},
  "extended_thinking": {"enabled": false},
  "secrets_source": "1password",
  "version": "1.1.0",
  "last_reviewed": "2026-05-22"
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "artefact_id": "x",
  "model": "claude-3-5-sonnet",
  "max_tokens": 999999,
  "shape": "batch",
  "max_turns": 100,
  "retry": {"enabled": false, "max_attempts": 0, "strategy": "none"},
  "caching": {"enabled": true, "block_token_size": 500, "ttl_seconds": 60},
  "tooling": {"tool_count": 25, "forced_tool": false},
  "secrets_source": "hardcoded"
}
]]></code>
    <note>artefact_id fails pattern; model not in enum (old name); max_tokens out of range; shape=batch with max_turns=100 is non-sensical (Batch has no turns); retry disabled with 0 attempts; caching block 500 tokens is below cacheable minimum; tool_count exceeds the recommended cap of 10; secrets_source not in enum; version + last_reviewed missing.</note>
  </example>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-claude-api.py">Validator that enforces this contract.</reference>

</text>
